text: Dmitry Kuskov (14 December 1876 - 11 October 1956) was a Russian sports shooter. He competed in six events at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1876 births Category:1956 deaths Category:Russian male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Russia Category:Shooters at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:People from Saint Petersburg
